  "subject": "Draft schema abstraction lib for review",
  "commit_message": "Draft schema abstraction lib for review\n\nIntroduction of a schema abstraction library which will implement an\ninterface by which clients can query the schema without needing to\nunderstand the complexity of loading and parsing OXM.  The library also\nabstracts away the concept of OXM such that OXM could be replaced by\nanother format for defining the schema without the calling client being\naware.\n\nPart of this submission includes the beginnings of an alternative schema\nformat (json instead of OXM).  That implementation is found in the\nschemaif.json package.  It is very much a work in progress.\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-2394\nChange-Id: I39101ca03c1b3231df52e472b4e1bc4928d12f38\nSigned-off-by: sblimkie <steven.blimkie@amdocs.com>\n",
